{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was literally walking on two left wooden shoes-- no, two right wooden shoes, because the left wooden-- the left shoe wouldn't fit me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I still have a raised arch, that my-- my left shoe is of a different size than my right shoe, because they didn't have shoes for me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But you made do because that's the best there was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I-- you kept on truckin'.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, anyhow--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I did not have that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have-- but-- we disappeared pretty soon, so I never found out if I-- if there were Nazi people around me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And keep in mind, at that time, I was-- when  I went underground I was eight years old-- nine-- eight or nine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the distinction of what was a Nazi or NSB or anything like that, I-- I did not understand-- had a full grasp of that distinction.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except I knew that I should make sure to avoid certain people, and I was told avoid that, avoid that, avoid that, avoid that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my-- my prime objective, just to avoid certain people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyhow, where were we?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the war you went back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was 14 years old, and I managed to convince my father to let me take music lessons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first instrument that I took was Hawaiian steel guitar, of all instruments.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about, oh, two years later or a year later-- I was 15 years old-- I had my first Hawaiian ensemble, and I played for the school, all the school thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then about a year later after that, I re-tuned my Hawaiian steel guitar to a regular guitar because I wasn't happy the way  the steel guitar was developing for me.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
